problem. Read this section to fully understand what it takes to be one of the board members of ASME.                      UIC Logo        Student Organizations    This website is produced and managed by an offical UIC student organization. The content of this site is not produced, edited, or endorsed by the university and it does not reflect the opinions of UIC administration.     American Society of Mechanical Engineers  Contact   Schwab Ho, Webmaster  cho208@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 